Westside Inbound

Description:

The Westside Inbound leaves the University Downtown Center and travels through Main Street in Binghamton and Floral Avenue in Johnson City enroute to campus.


Reminder: All Inbound buses at the University Downtown Center return to campus.

Operation Time:

Weekdays:
7:20 A.M. to 12:05 A.M. (Monday - Thursdays) or 11:35 P.M. (Fridays)


Weekends:
9:05 A.M. to 11:35 P.M.

Notes:

Scroll below for a graphic map of the Westside Inbound, its schedule, and the stops along its route.


For Friday and Saturday nights after 12:00 A.M. please refer to the Late Night WS Inbound, unless otherwise posted.
